---
import Card from "../../ui/Card.astro";
import Heading from "../../ui/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../../ui/Text.astro";
---

<div class="lg:w-2/3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-6 lg:grid-rows-2">

  <!-- TOP CARD -->
  <Card class="card-glow-hover card-transparent glow-top-philosophy relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-6 min-h-[360px]">
    <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 h-full">

      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center px-8 py-10 max-w-xl">
        <Heading level={3} class="mb-3 text-2xl">
          Risk-first mindset
        </Heading>
        <Text muted class="text-sm lg:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Cada decisión parte del riesgo asumido, no del beneficio esperado. Si el riesgo no está perfectamente definido, la operación simplemente no existe. El control del riesgo es el origen de todo.
        </Text>
      </div>

      <div class="relative h-full">
        <img
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6801648/pexels-photo-6801648.jpeg"
          alt=""
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
  </Card>

  <!-- BOTTOM LEFT -->
  <Card class="card-glow-hover card-transparent glow-bottom-philosophy relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-4 min-h-[300px] flex flex-col">
    <div class="relative z-10 px-6 py-6">
      <Heading level={3} class="mb-2 text-xl">
        Capital preservation
      </Heading>
      <Text muted class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Proteger el capital es siempre la prioridad. Sin capital no existe operativa. La consistencia a largo plazo importa más que cualquier resultado aislado.
      </Text>
    </div>

    <div class="relative flex-1">
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4386366/pexels-photo-4386366.jpeg"
        alt=""
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15"
      />
    </div>
  </Card>

  <!-- BOTTOM RIGHT -->
  <Card class="card-glow-hover card-transparent glow-bottom-philosophy-right relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-2 min-h-[300px] flex flex-col">
    <div class="relative z-10 px-6 py-6">
      <Heading level={3} class="mb-2 text-xl">
        Process-driven trading
      </Heading>
      <Text muted class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Operamos procesos definidos, no emociones. El sistema manda siempre, independientemente del resultado de una sola operación.
      </Text>
    </div>

    <div class="relative flex-1">
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6801874/pexels-photo-6801874.jpeg"
        alt=""
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15"
      />
    </div>
  </Card>

</div>

<script is:inline>
  document.querySelectorAll(".card-glow-hover").forEach(function (card) {
    card.addEventListener("mousemove", function (e) {
      const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
      card.style.setProperty("--x", (e.clientX - rect.left) + "px");
      card.style.setProperty("--y", (e.clientY - rect.top) + "px");
    });
  });
</script>
